# Implementation Plan - Dark-Themed Admin Dashboard UI

Create a fully dark-themed, professional Admin Dashboard for the Campus Placement Job Portal using React and Tailwind CSS.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Tailwind CSS & Theme Foundation
Update the project to support Tailwind CSS and define the dark theme color palette.

#### [MODIFY] [package.json](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/package.json)
- Add `tailwindcss`, `postcss`, and `autoprefixer` to devDependencies.

#### [NEW] [tailwind.config.js](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/tailwind.config.js)
- Configure Tailwind with the requested dark theme colors:
  - Background: `#0f172a` (slate-900)
  - Card background: `#1e293b` (slate-800)
  - Primary: Indigo/Blue
  - Borders: `#334155` (slate-700)

#### [MODIFY] [index.css](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/src/index.css)
- Add Tailwind directives.
- Set global dark theme styles (background, text color).
- Remove conflicting light theme styles.

---

### [Component] Core Layout Components
Create reusable layout components that follow the dark theme requirements.

#### [NEW] [AdminLayout.jsx](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/src/components/admin/AdminLayout.jsx)
- A new layout wrapper for admin routes with a fixed dark sidebar and a scrollable main content area.

#### [NEW] [Sidebar.jsx](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/src/components/admin/Sidebar.jsx)
- A vertical sidebar with active link highlighting and smooth transitions.

---

