### [Component] Reusable UI Components
Create a set of common components to ensure consistency across the dashboard.

#### [NEW] [Card.jsx](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/src/components/ui/Card.jsx), [Button.jsx](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/src/components/ui/Button.jsx), [Input.jsx](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/src/components/ui/Input.jsx), [Table.jsx](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/src/components/ui/Table.jsx), [Modal.jsx](file:///c:/Users/USER/JOBPORTAL%20-%20Copy/vite-job/src/components/ui/Modal.jsx)
- Reusable Tailwind-based components mirroring the requested "deep dark" aesthetic.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- No existing automated tests were found.
- Verification will be done through manual browser testing.

### Manual Verification
1. **Theme Consistency**: Ensure across all admin pages that the background is `#0f172a` and cards are `#1e293b`.
2. **Responsiveness**: Test the dashboard on different screen sizes (Desktop, Tablet, Mobile) using browser devtools.
3. **Interactions**:
   *   Verify Sidebar navigation works correctly and highlights active routes.
   *   Verify Hover effects on cards, buttons, and table rows.
   *   Verify Modal backdrop blur and centering.
4. **Functionality**: Ensure CRUD operations (Manage Users, Jobs, Students) still work correctly with the new UI.
